cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.ET 

The paper discusses the development of fast algorithms for efficient approximation of 2-D DCT transforms for video processing systems, which is a common topic in the computer science sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM), computer vision (cs.CV), information theory (cs.IT), and signal processing (cs.AR). Additionally, the paper discusses the physical realization of the proposed DCT approximation using FPGA technology and CMOS technology, which falls under the sub-category of electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET).
